	(119,2,'2017-12-24 22:33:38','2017-12-24 22:33:38','The avant-garde looks of the all new Pershing 70 will impress both loyal and new fans to the brand. A dynamic profile and innovative design are enhanced by two large structural wings that give the yacht a truly breathtaking appearance on the water, and a truly unique personality like no other. This yacht represents a new generation of Pershing and captivates owners who seek a yacht with unique style that is recognizable at a glance and is the essence of elegance and speed, power and beauty, technology and safety.','Luxury Yacht Pershing 70','','publish','closed','closed','','luxury-yacht-pershing-70','','','2017-12-24 22:38:16','2017-12-24 22:38:16','',0,'http://localhost/fct001/?post_type=fct_contest&#038;p=119',0,'fct_contest','',0),
